        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1268120325" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12120059687862793086">A compilation of short stories, many of which Rosamunde wrote for Good Housekeeping magazine in the 1950&apos;s. They take you back to a time where true love could be found in a look or holding of hands.<br/><br/>This is so Brittish in writing that a cuppa tea and a biscuit should accompany the reader to a pretty garden to read.<br/><br/>Abosolutely loved it refreshing for a change.</span>
