        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2438219651" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1605436340290511880">Rosamunde Pilcher is my comfort food. When I am feeling down, I read her stories and feel better. They are not complex adventures in far off places. They are just regular people living their lives and dealing with everyday problems we can all relate to.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


